Logo for a tech company named "asperion" in all lowercase using the Proxima Nova font, set against a transparent background. The typography is modern, minimal, and professional. All letters are filled with a **flat,  blue tone** for a refined, corporate-friendly look — no gradients, glow, or effects. The dot on the "i" is a **matte solid red**, sized precisely to match the font’s original dot height and centered as per Proxima Nova’s type design. The logo is intended for high-clarity, multi-platform branding and works seamlessly across digital and print environments.
